## Backend environment variables

PORT=8080

# Optional MongoDB connection (only needed if you add DB-backed features)
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://<user>:<password>@<cluster>/<db>?retryWrites=true&w=majority

# CORS: allow your Vercel domain (comma-separated for multiple)
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173

# Optional GitHub token for proxy endpoint
GITHUB_TOKEN=

